<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 09:13:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>达赖喇嘛89岁生日否认健康谣言</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/dalai-lama-dismisses-health-rumours-89th-birthday-2024-07-06/</link><description>达赖喇嘛周六表示，他正在从膝盖手术中恢复，感觉“身体健康”，在他89岁生日之际否认了有关健康状况不佳的谣言。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 08:35:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/dalai-lama-dismisses-health-rumours-89th-birthday-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾海岸警卫队称中国在南海抛锚“巨轮”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-anchors-monster-ship-in-south-china-sea-philippine-coast-guard-says-2024-07-06/</link><description>菲律宾海岸警卫队（PCG）周六表示，中国最大的海岸警卫队船只已停泊在南中国海的马尼拉专属经济区（EEZ），旨在恐吓其较小的亚洲邻国。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 07:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-anchors-monster-ship-in-south-china-sea-philippine-coast-guard-says-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国第二大淡水湖溃坝后居民搬迁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/residents-relocated-after-dam-breach-chinas-second-largest-freshwater-lake-2024-07-06/</link><description>中国官方媒体周六称，中国南部第二大淡水湖的水位冲破堤坝后，约 5,700 名居民被重新安置，救援人员则忙于控制水流造成的进一步损失。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 05:53:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/residents-relocated-after-dam-breach-chinas-second-largest-freshwater-lake-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>台湾调查与中国打交道的高级官员涉嫌受贿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-probes-senior-official-who-deals-with-china-over-bribery-suspicions-2024-07-06/</link><description>台湾检察官周六表示，他们正在调查一名高级官员和执政的民进党（DPP）成员，该官员因涉嫌贿赂而与中国打交道。他说他没有做错任何事。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 04:04:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-probes-senior-official-who-deals-with-china-over-bribery-suspicions-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年温网：第 6 天德约科维奇和贾布尔的比赛顺序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/djokovic-faces-tricky-popyrin-test-wimbledon-third-round-2024-07-05/</link><description>温布尔登第三轮比赛将于周六在全英俱乐部继续进行，世界顶级球员将在伦敦争夺大满贯的荣耀。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 21:37:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/djokovic-faces-tricky-popyrin-test-wimbledon-third-round-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国调查中国游泳运动员兴奋剂案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/us-investigating-chinese-swimmer-doping-case-2024-07-05/</link><description>世界水上运动协会执行董事布伦特·诺维茨基 (Brent Nowicki) 已被美国政府传唤，要求就 23 名中国游泳运动员在东京奥运会前几周违禁药物检测呈阳性后如何避免受到处罚的调查作证。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 14:11:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/us-investigating-chinese-swimmer-doping-case-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，欧洲顶级干邑生产商将出席中国反倾销调查会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/europes-top-cognac-makers-will-attend-china-meeting-anti-dumping-probe-source-2024-07-05/</link><description>一位业内消息人士称，欧洲主要干邑白兰地生产商将于 7 月 18 日在北京出席中国对该行业反倾销调查的听证会，这是自今年早些时候调查开始以来，他们第一次有机会亲自为自己辩护。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 12:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/europes-top-cognac-makers-will-attend-china-meeting-anti-dumping-probe-source-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>AK党官员表示，中国广汽集团与土耳其汽车制造商TOGG就电动汽车进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-gac-turkish-carmaker-togg-ev-talks-says-ak-party-official-2024-07-05/</link><description>土耳其执政党正义与发展党副主席扎菲尔·西拉卡亚 (Zafer Sirakaya) 表示，中国汽车制造商广汽集团 (GAC) 正在与土耳其电动汽车 (EV) 制造商 TOGG 就建立合资企业的可能性进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:57:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-gac-turkish-carmaker-togg-ev-talks-says-ak-party-official-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>国泰航空将回购香港政府剩余50%优先股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-buy-back-remaining-50-hk-governments-preference-shares-2024-07-05/</link><description>香港国泰航空周五表示，将回购7月31日向香港特别行政区政府发行的剩余50%优先股。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-buy-back-remaining-50-hk-governments-preference-shares-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国监管机构誓言严厉打击资本市场欺诈行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-regulator-vows-clamp-down-harder-capital-market-fraud-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周五誓言要加大力度打击金融欺诈行为，并表示正在推动对违法者进行更严厉的惩罚，以期重振人们对中国陷入困境的股市的信心。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:07:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-regulator-vows-clamp-down-harder-capital-market-fraud-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>汽车制造商回应欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-respond-eu-tariffs-chinese-made-evs-2024-07-05/</link><description>随着欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税于周五生效，一些汽车制造商一直在考虑是否提高价格或采取其他措施来应对。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:05:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-respond-eu-tariffs-chinese-made-evs-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金 高位金价抑制印度和中国的经济活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-high-gold-prices-dull-activity-india-china-2024-07-05/</link><description>印度的实物黄金交易商因价格高企而连续第九周提供折扣，因为他们等待即将到来的预算中可能降低进口关税，而最大的消费国中国也看到需求疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:51:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-high-gold-prices-dull-activity-india-china-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>蔚来首席财务官冯锋辞职，电动汽车制造商任命内部人士为继任者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nio-cfo-feng-steps-down-ev-maker-appoints-insider-successor-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车周五表示，冯伟以个人原因辞去首席财务官一职，立即生效。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nio-cfo-feng-steps-down-ev-maker-appoints-insider-successor-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：欧洲就中国老一代芯片征求行业意见</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/europe-seeks-industry-views-chinas-older-generation-chips-2024-07-05/</link><description>两位知情人士告诉路透社，欧盟委员会已开始征求该地区半导体行业对中国扩大老一代计算机芯片生产的看法。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:20:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/europe-seeks-industry-views-chinas-older-generation-chips-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：劳工焦点——美国就业、英国新政府</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-05/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:05:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>